Camomile is an application that turns off the screen of your mac.

The name is inspired of the camomile tea. Besides being my favorite tea, it makes you sleep as well =)

Download it from here: https://github.com/Dimme/Camomile.app/blob/master/Camomile-1.0.dmg?raw=true

